enhanced_by.reason: The add method populates the hResults map, which is used by getResultValueMap to generate the result map.
The merge method combines results from another ValidatorResults object into hResults, affecting the output of getResultValueMap.
Both methods interact with the hResults map and can be used to verify the state and content of the results map.
getPropertyNames provides the keys of the hResults map, which can be used to verify the keys in the result map returned by getResultValueMap.
